{{Quote|You are unclean. You are accursed. Leave Tilverton. Your presence is foul and unwanted.|Phylanna to Kelemvor, after discovering he is a [[werepanther]].}}

During the [[Time of Troubles]] in the {{YearlinkName|1358}}, Phylanna spent a passionate night with the mercenary [[Kelemvor Lyonsbane]]. The morning after, she was dazed by the [[jackalwere]] [[Torrence]], who attempted to lure out Kelemvor's lycanthropic [[panther]] form. Phylanna was aghast at Kelemvor's eventual transformation, telling her once-lover he was accursed and should leave Tilverton for good.

Before Kelemvor left the city, Phylanna told a group of the Gondar faithful that he was a "monster" that had to be killed to earn back the divine presence of Gond.
